{"tid":589710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【沙士15●世紀病毒2D睇】 從未消失！若變種或再傳人","createTime":"2018-03-12T04:51:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-12T04:52:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bf3125a0afe6d3deb8aca9f34d8136b034617f85","tid":589710,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T04:51:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180312/20329548\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180312%2F20329548&d=Jd8DbL3f2CtNCvN5tg%2Fm1Rv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=20c2d0d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180312%2F20329548&h=30ffb1cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180312/20329548</a><br />\n<br />\n【沙士15●世紀病毒2D睇】<br />\n從未消失！若變種或再傳人<br />\n<br />\n要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n2003年襲港的沙士，源自蝙蝠身上的冠狀病毒，但為何動物身上的病毒，會變成人類殺手？關鍵原來在一隻動物身上。15年過去，病毒從未消失，為何仍有機會威脅人類？《蘋果》2D睇為你解構，去片！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n\t醫生冒險解剖八遺體揭開謎團<br />\n要聞 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t獨自留院　不見家人三個月<br />\n要聞 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t赴中東取駱駝糞研究新沙士<br />\n要聞 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t貼身照顧病人　前線醫護中招<br />\n要聞 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t病毒至今存蝙蝠體內　隨時再次傳人　港大研發萬用藥物應對<br />\n要聞 5小時前"},{"pid":"ffade256b138705f5956e4cea905df95abf0daad","tid":589710,"uid":8867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T04:52:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}